literals: "This app uses config/default.json as default config file. Use config/default.json.sample as a base "
"to create your own configuration with correct AWS credentials."
"Config file name can be overridden by -c or --config-file command line argument"
"Error: Invalid AWS credentials in the config file"
comments: this will read the default configuration file
show help message if -h or --help is present
override configuration if -c or --config-file is present
